											<div class="cell auto tertiary-story">
					<div class="story-img-container">
						<a href="https://lithub.com/a-miserable-day-in-the-life-of-an-unwilling-homeschooler/" title="A (Miserable) Day in the Life of an Unwilling Homeschooler"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/storms-on-the-plains-1-300x300.jpg"></a>
